{"_id":"0fXnvduqtkSpdB7n","name":"Rapscallion","type":"class","img":"systems/pirateborg/tokens/rapscallion.png","data":{"description":"<p>A sneaky, cutthroat scallywag good at backstabbing, breaking &amp; entering, stealing, cheating, and escaping. Found in taverns, shadows, and shallow graves.</p>\n<p>You will need a deck of playing cards.</p>","flavorText":"A sneaky, cutthroat scallywag good at backstabbing, breaking & entering, stealing, cheating, and escaping. Found in taverns, shadows, and shallow graves.\n\nYou will need a deck of playing cards.","luckDie":"1d2","startingArmorTableFormula":"1d6","startingWeaponTableFormula":"1d6","startingHatTableFormula":"1d10","startingAbilityScoreFormula":"3d6","startingAgilityBonus":"+2","startingPresenceBonus":"","startingStrengthBonus":"-1","startingToughnessBonus":"-1","startingSpiritBonus":"","startingHitPoints":"1d8","startingItems":"pirateborg.class-rapscallion;Deck of Cards\npirateborg.class-rapscallion;Drinking Grog\npirateborg.class-rapscallion;Joker Table","startingRolls":"pirateborg.rolls-rapscallion;Features;1","startingMacro":"","gettingBetterRolls":"pirateborg.rolls-rapscallion;Features;1","gettingBetterMacro":"","useExtraResource":false,"extraResourceNameSingular":"","extraResourceNamePlural":"","extraResourceFormula":"","extraResourceFormulaLabel":"","extraResourceTestFormula":"","extraResourceTestFormulaLabel":"","requireBaseClass":false,"isBaseClass":false,"characterGeneratorMacro":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6E1mLAFydr0EDuPa","name":"Rope Monkey","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>You&rsquo;re as nimble in the rigging as you are on the deck.</p>\n<p>If you attack after swinging, jumping, or making an acrobatic maneuver, test Agility DR10 to automatically hit and deal +2 damage.</p>\n<p>If taken again: increase extra damage by +1.</p>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":0,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HMT5ThVUlSdqrZeE","name":"Back Stabber","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>If you attack by surprise (from hiding, distracted enemy, etc.) lower the attack DR by 2 and deal d2 extra damage.</p>\n<p>If taken again, draw a card.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Black: Lower DR by 1.</li>\n<li>Red: Increase damage die [d2&gt;d4&gt;d6&gt;d8].</li>\n<li>Joker: Both</li>\n</ul>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":0,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KLIZ1qvZj09FHC19","name":"Grog Brewer","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>Each day you can brew d4 servings of potent grog. You can soak melee weapons in it to use as a poison.</p>\n<p>Grog in a wound: Toughness DR14 or -d6 HP.</p>\n<p>If taken again, draw a card.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Black: +2 to DR.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Red: Increase damage die [d6&gt;d8&gt;d10&gt;d12].</li>\n<li>Joker: Both</li>\n</ul>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":null,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":"","startingBonusRolls":"","flavorText":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OkZdivv3kUbcZVGM","name":"Joker Table","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>1. The Devil comes for your soul. You are sucked into a fiery portal. This is the end of your story.</p>\n<p>2-9. Lose all of your remaining luck points.</p>\n<p>10-19. Regain 2 luck points.</p>\n<p>20. Gain 4 Luck points (to a max of 4)</p>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":null,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-rapscallion;Joker Table","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":"","startingBonusRolls":"","flavorText":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sYUKPmVVlxHlrNMC","name":"Lucky Devil","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>When you use the Devil&rsquo;s Luck, draw a playing card:</p>\n<p><em>9+: Regain 1 Luck. </em></p>\n<p><em>Joker: Roll on the Joker Table.</em></p>\n<p>If taken again: Lower the card number needed to regain luck by 1.</p>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":null,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":"","startingBonusRolls":"","flavorText":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uEPa3dSpWelONDim","name":"Burglar","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/misc/class-feature.png","data":{"description":"<p>You begin with lock picks.</p>\n<p>Pickpocket, disarm an enemy, or disable a trap: -4 to DR.</p>\n<p>If taken again: additional -2 to DR.</p>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":0,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":"pirateborg.equipment-gear;Lock picks","startingBonusRolls":"","flavorText":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uTBQYaz7kKpbxlJp","name":"Drinking Grog","type":"feature","img":"systems/pirateborg/icons/classes/rapscallion/beer-stein.png","data":{"description":"<p>Test Toughness DR8 + [Number of drinks in the last hour] to heal d4 HP. Fail and you vomit for d2 rounds.</p>\n<p>Agility is -1 for each drink (lasts one hour per drink)</p>","featureType":"Class","maxQuantity":null,"quantity":1,"actionMacro":"pirateborg.macros-pirateborg;Generic Item","actionMacroLabel":"Use","startingBonusItems":"","startingBonusRolls":"","flavorText":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"pdXclp2r5tiEF79G":3},"flags":{}}
